This paper discusses SQL Injection attacks and their detection and prevention techniques, which are related to computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of classical and modern approaches for detection and prevention, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of SQL Injection attacks on websites, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
